USER-ROLE: INSERT INTO user_role (roleName, description, createdById, lastModifiedById) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?)
USER: INSERT INTO user (userName, password, userRoleId, createdById, lastModifiedById) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?)

CATEGORY-TYPE: INSERT INTO category_type (categoryTypeName, createdById, lastModifiedById) VALUES (?, ?, ?)
